text:
There's a problem where EU consent options are overlaid by the chat bubble due to a nuclear z-index solution. It's easily fixable but it shouldn't be this way.
```div#hs-eu-cookie-confirmation {
...
  z-index: 100000000 !important;
...
}

#HubSpot-messages-iframe-container {
...
  z-index: 2147483647;
...
}```
fix is obv having `#HubSpot-messages-iframe-container { z-index: 99999999 !important }`
edit. better fix
```.hs-cookie-notification-position-bottom:not([style*="display: none;"]) ~ #HubSpot-messages-iframe-container {
    display: none !important ;
}```
